erse ($z<1$). Finally, we show that the clustering of\nphotometrically selected PSBs are consistent with them being direct descendants\nof highly dust-enshrouded sub-millimetre galaxies (SMGs), providing tantalising\nevidence for the oft-speculated evolutionary pathway from starburst to\nquiescence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Apr 2021 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-19"}
