wledge. Our model achieves\nstate-of-the-art performance on multiple FSOD benchmarks over most of the shots\nand metrics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Apr 2021 19:01:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Jun 2021 17:30:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 17 Dec 2021 06:11:50 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 17:33:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-03"}
