 to compute the energy released by\ndisorder induced heating using the pair correlation function. This disorder\ninduced heating energy was found to scale very near the theoretical result for\nstationary ultracold plasmas, and it accounts for over half of the emittance\ngrowth above mean-field simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Apr 2021 22:04:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
