ough DeepSpeed, a deep learning optimization library that makes distributed\ntraining easy, efficient, and effective.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Apr 2021 02:22:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-19"}
