 outlet) for the case of soft particles with\nlow friction coefficient, and proposed a phenomenological formulation that\npredicts the linear decrease of the flow rate with decreasing filling height.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Apr 2021 15:57:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-19"}
